      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between aesthetic appeal and mechanical reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, showing only minor signs of careful road use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free, with the leather and trim showing minimal wear and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, this car has been kept on a strict maintenance schedule; the engine pulls strong, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It is a well-maintained, dependable driver that looks great in any driveway.",
